<strong>Getting The Sync</strong>
All of the assets (models sounds etc) for Double Action are in a shared BitTorrent Sync folder. Anybody can download these files to access them. There are two ways of getting at them. The first is by downloading <a href="http://www.bittorrent.com/sync/">BitTorrent Sync</a> and using the read-only secret: BPOJT55Z4BFMS6H3OH6QR7IFHZN3LDGP5 to start downloading the project.

The second way is to access the files through HTTP here at <a href="http://sync.doubleactiongame.com/">http://sync.doubleactiongame.com/</a>

